&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide advanced technical support to our growing customer base via multiple channels (Zendesk, Zoom, Slack).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot complex issues spanning software configuration, networking, and integrations — including analyzing logs, reproducing issues, and debugging code.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure our customers achieve fast and lasting success with DataHub.&lt;/li&gt;
