&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience building and operating multi-tenant SaaS platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background in developing customer-facing deployment and management tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of data infrastructure and metadata management systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
