&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is where infrastructure meets impact.&lt;/strong&gt; The metadata layer you&#39;ll build will directly power the next generation of AI systems at massive scale. Your code will determine how safely and effectively thousands of organizations deploy AI, affecting millions of users worldwide.&lt;/p&gt;
