&lt;li&gt;Scalable, fault-tolerant ingestion systems for enterprise-scale metadata&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clean, intuitive APIs for our connector ecosystem&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Event-driven architectures for real-time metadata processing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Schema mapping between diverse systems and DataHub&#39;s unified model&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Versioning systems for AI assets (training data, model weights, embeddings)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
