&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years building production-grade distributed systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced Python expertise with a focus on API design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with high-scale data processing or integration frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong systems knowledge and distributed architecture experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A track record of solving complex technical challenges&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus Points&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
